          "name": "Dijon mustard",
          "quantity": "2",
          "measurement": "tablespoons"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "instructionText": "Lay out plastic wrap and arrange prosciutto slices. Spread mushroom mixture over prosciutto and place beef in the center. Use the plastic wrap to roll tightly and chill.",
